quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,By the fig and by the olive
  95,2,by the mount of Sinai
  95,3,and by this city of security (Makkah)
  95,4,"Surely, We have created people in the best stature"
  95,5,then We will reduce it to the lowest of the low
  95,6,"except those who believe (in Islam) and do righteous deeds, then for them will be a reward without end (Paradise)"
  95,7,"So, what causes you (disbelievers) to deny about the Day of Judgment"
  95,8,Is not Allah the best of the judges